spotify.title: Spotify 2.0
spotify.description:
A sleek front-end redesign of the Spotify desktop interface. 
 This project is a work in progress and is still under development.
 It is not a clone of the original Spotify UI.
 It is a clone of the UI of the Spotify web player.
 It is a clone of the UI of the Spotify desktop player.
